name: Leonardo
description: Leonardo Skin Care Group is developing, importing and marketing an equipment combined with Nano-technological preparations for a range of medical cosmetic treatments and beauty care, primarily: hair removal (patent), body sculpting, skin rejuvenation and tightening, wrinkle removal, anti-aging as well as a wide range of other treatments that offer a perfect solution for various problems such as acne, cellulite, toenail fungus.
